{"type": "article", "id": 16748, "title": "工作型桌椅", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-29T07:20:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122437qcMuGLDgTEY9K7Vm.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这套桌椅来自日本的建筑事务所 Schemata Architects，他们要为一个前身是教室的工作室定制。在四根木制的腿上用了白色的钢管做支撑，更加稳固且显得简洁有序。此外，木材和钢材，浅棕色和白色对比，让这套桌椅看起来很清爽。<a href=\"http://schemata.jp/w-workshop-furniture-for-studio-renova-ring/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144036LrWBeGH6CaNxcn8Y.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144037Mxjd2TqhB7yKv8kP.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144038kRGge6C3dM5UQKN9.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144039tTOfbB94nERhJ7cX.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"546\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}